body:
## What's Changed

This version brings a major change : we can now parse integers, as well as floating-point numbers. 

* float_common.h:237:52 Value stored to 'input_num' is never read by @Coeur in https://github.com/fastfloat/fast_float/pull/224
* fix for 32-bit Visual Studio when not set to round to nearest by @lemire in https://github.com/fastfloat/fast_float/pull/225
* Fix for ARM SIMD by @mayawarrier in https://github.com/fastfloat/fast_float/pull/230
* from_chars integer parser by @mayawarrier in https://github.com/fastfloat/fast_float/pull/231


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/fastfloat/fast_float/compare/v5.3.0...v6.0.0
